<i>noun</i>: 형용 [형용], 초상 [초상], 서술 [서ː술], 묘사 [묘ː사], 기술 [기술] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>형용 [형용]</dt><br>
<dd>1. shape; figure; form</dd><br>
<dd>사물의 생긴 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>The appearance or shape of an object.</dd><br>
<dd>2. appearance; looks</dd><br>
<dd>사람의 생긴 모양이나 모습.</dd><br>
<dd>The appearance or features of a person.</dd><br>
<dd>3. description; depiction; portrayal</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 글, 동작 등으로 사람이나 사물의 모양을 나타냄.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of expressing the appearance of a person or thing through words, writing, gestures, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>초상 [초상]</dt><br>
<dd>1. portrait</dd><br>
<dd>사진, 그림 등에 나타낸 사람의 얼굴이나 모습.</dd><br>
<dd>The face or appearance of someone expressed in a photograph, a work of drawing or painting, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>2. reflection; depiction</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 것에 비춰지거나 생각되는 모습.</dd><br>
<dd>The appearance that is reflected on something or is thought of.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>서술 [서ː술]</dt><br>
<dd>description; depiction; narration</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 사실, 사건, 생각 등을 논리나 순서에 따라 말하거나 적음.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of writing or saying a fact, incident, thought, etc., according to a certain logic or order.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>묘사 [묘ː사]</dt><br>
<dd>description; portrayal; depiction</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 대상을 있는 그대로 자세하게 말이나 글로 표현하거나 그림으로 그림.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of giving a detailed account of a certain object in spoken or written words, or expressing it in paintings as it stands.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>기술 [기술]</dt><br>
<dd>depiction</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 사실을 있는 그대로 적음. 또는 그런 기록.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of writing a certain fact as it is, or such a record.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>